HEADWORD: Fluffy
<hw>Fluff"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Fluffier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
